===Alternative forms===
Note difference between Chinese form, which uses {{l|mul|曾}}, and Japanese {{w|shinjitai}} which uses {{l|mul|曽}}.

In Korea, the upper right component is {{l|mul|八}} instead of {{l|mul|丷}}, which is also the historical form found in the {{w|Kangxi dictionary}}.

